query:
SELECT 
  a.id as assetId, 
  a.name as assetName, 
  CAST(a.replacementValue AS CHAR) as assetCRV,
  p.id as projectId,
  CAST(p.currentReplacementValue AS CHAR) as projectCRV,
  CAST(p.deferredMaintenanceCost AS CHAR) as projectDMC
FROM assets a
INNER JOIN projects p ON a.projectId = p.id
WHERE p.deletedAt IS NULL
LIMIT 5;
